subsection.def:
controlled substance (受管制物質) means Class 3 dangerous goods or Class 3A
                                dangerous goods, as defined by section 2 of the Dangerous
                                Goods (Application and Exemption) Regulation 2012 (Cap. 295 sub. leg. E);

paragraph.content:
